name: Full Skatepark Index, United States, 2008
description: This data set includes an index of all the current skateparks in the United States.  On the SkateBoardPark.com website visitors can create a user name and login. The user then can input the name, and address of a skatepark.  There is also an area for description and if the park cost money to skate in.  It is a current source because skaters constantly add new skatepark locations when they are opened to the public. The addresses of the skateparks were geocoded and are represented as point data.
